				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Hello,
<br />

<br />
I am a webhost with a lot of phpBB users who install the standard phpBB and clog up my maillog by getting attacked.
<br />

<br />
Since your standard license allows &quot;running on any number of computers&quot; I am sure that I could simply buy one copy and get it to run on many sites, but I wanted to make sure this is kosher by you.
<br />

<br />
As a side note, I also often run scripts that auto-install scripts like this onto my user boards (a little bit BOFH, but I do what is necessary).
<br />

<br />
Are these allowable via your license?</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
